{"tid":730631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿戰：別期望特朗普收手　對港政策恐有變","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T01:58:53.000Z","uid":174649,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3a06e1408b6e04271b497bb7448f1742ea4b27","tid":730631,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180705/photo/bkn-20180705194213631-0705_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180705210538\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180705%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180705194213631-0705_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180705210538&h=7f05afbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國外貿銀行亞太區經濟學家吳卓殷表示，中美貿易戰進一步升溫的機會不小。美國總統特朗普的言論「望落去好似好唔consistent(一致)咁，其實好consistent地針對住美國對中國不滿嘅地方」，中美短期內縱有談判也難望有很大轉機，或許餘下總值160億美元中國商品加徵25%關稅不久也會落實，時間在11月美國中期選舉之前。額外2,000億美元的中國商品亦有可能加徵關稅，始終中國已揚言會還擊。 <br />\n<br />\n他續指，儘管中國最近已經公布金融等行業的開放措施，但外資公司即使有較大股權，實際經營環境下又是否自由，美方會比較在意。此外，中美貿易戰也是「科技戰」，美國希望於科技等爭議的談判主導權。中國針對美國進口商品採取金額上以牙還牙的策略恐怕難令特朗普「收手」，況且中國恐怕沒有更多美國進口貨用來還擊。 <br />\n<br />\n吳卓殷認為，中美貿易戰對兩國都有損害，雖然可以繞經第三個市場出口到對方，但原料輸入成本上漲也不利企業盈利。他不認為中國經濟增長會出現「斷崖式下跌」，但中國經濟大部分是傳統行業，科技及新能源等新興產業未必可以抵銷傳統行業所受的衝擊，而且中國出口不少來自外資企業在華分支，中美貿易糾紛也會牽連內地就業和消費，就像中興通訊(00763)佔深圳工業產值比重不低。 <br />\n<br />\n談到中美貿易戰對香港的影響，他表示暫時未有明確估計，要視乎兩國緊張關係升溫到甚麼地步，但始終香港息口跟美國，經濟跟中國，很難獨善其身，更大風險在於美國會否改變將香港與中國分別處理的政策。 <br />\n－－－－－－"},{"pid":"b88d8b01099114b0e2671503a519e7defcdee013","tid":730631,"uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"香港是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01967d883f51d23f258c5be9d14bf40b1a1fd7cc","tid":730631,"uid":75877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"幾時搞鳩香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53cb14bef3f3d068f602af8738bcc6d8eefa796","tid":730631,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e595ed9cee7600fdbe10e795b5eed4c5254141d8","tid":730631,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01967d883f51d23f258c5be9d14bf40b1a1fd7cc","tid":730631,"uid":75877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"幾時搞鳩香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"想同中國分享榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ec27f09ab2c599822ccbe42e588ab1596fac82","tid":730631,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://post76.hk/data/attachment/forum/201504/14/113621zrgkgsqbfggfzvsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201504%2F14%2F113621zrgkgsqbfggfzvsg.jpg&h=2b9e2fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/finance/images/stories/1/2015/04/4128e320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Ffinance%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F1%2F2015%2F04%2F4128e320.jpg&h=a4ea000f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a4032897fb11d3c964f1350a16500ef64ebbd7","tid":730631,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"對港政策恐有變, 中國成最大贏家."},{"pid":"4c78340fe16bae5057f20c50e456e31bd5e73e49","tid":730631,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"全世界都係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170f786f60031153843fb8e673e94d14f83a87da","tid":730631,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:58:53.000Z","m